metadata.name: Starboy
metadata.description:
Starboy is a frame taken from Renaissance Malfunction's 'Wee, Kin, Star 'nd Kane Boy' NFT, which is limited to 10 pieces and intended for Huda Velvet friends and the VLVT Collective community.

Renaissance Malfunction is a unique NFT collection that redefines the art spectrum by fusing classic realism with modern glitch, grain, and trash art elements. Each 1/1 piece serves as a daring statement about the beauty of imperfection.

https://twitter.com/KingHudaPaints
